    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/34d2c6b51836e8eebef52471ce48b7da.poster.avif?t=1763383159\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/34d2c6b51836e8eebef52471ce48b7da.webm?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/34d2c6b51836e8eebef52471ce48b7da.mp4?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Nanali in another world是一个迷人的益智平台游戏，玩家将导航一个分为两个维度的世界，每个维度都充满了自己的危险和秘密。 通过控制女主角，纳纳利，你可以在这些现实之间切换，让你发现独特的路径和解决方案，通过水平的进步。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/4c37c344f49699dbfe48feb7e7ef9211.poster.avif?t=1763383159\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/4c37c344f49699dbfe48feb7e7ef9211.webm?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/4c37c344f49699dbfe48feb7e7ef9211.mp4?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏的每个区域都充满了互动元素，复杂的谜题和聪明的陷阱，需要快速反应和深思熟虑的策略。 通过利用尺寸力学,你将避免危险,解锁新的领域,并解决逻辑挑战.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/20567dda652a2a43190644c1c25ac6b1.poster.avif?t=1763383159\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/20567dda652a2a43190644c1c25ac6b1.webm?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/20567dda652a2a43190644c1c25ac6b1.mp4?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏的视觉风格以复古像素艺术呈现，唤起经典平台游戏的氛围。 结合动态的游戏和令人兴奋的机制之间的切换世界，纳纳利在另一个世界提供了一个独特的游戏体验拼图和平台爱好者。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/97ead1c3b4d45ca5726ea24f29a8d788.poster.avif?t=1763383159\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/97ead1c3b4d45ca5726ea24f29a8d788.webm?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207060/extras/97ead1c3b4d45ca5726ea24f29a8d788.mp4?t=1763383159\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纳纳利在另一个世界的主要特征:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>维度切换机制：在两个平行世界之间切换的能力是游戏的核心机制。 它允许玩家找到新的路径，解决难题，并绕过陷阱，使每个级别独特和战略吸引力。<br></li><li>不同的水平和不断增加的难度：游戏提供了广泛的挑战，随着你的进步变得更加困难。 陷阱和谜题不仅需要逻辑思维，还需要巧妙地利用维度切换来成功克服它们。<br></li><li>复古像素图形：游戏风格的复古像素艺术，这给它的魅力经典平台游戏和增加视觉吸引力。<br></li><li>大气配乐：音乐和声音效果增强了对游戏世界的沉浸感，营造出冒险和神秘感。</li></ul>",
